data.description: Redland & Homestead Living w/o city RE tax. This Super 3 bed 2 bath has an open, split-bdrm floor plan, giving you flex spaces. From the Foyer, the Living Rm is on the left w/Bamboo Floors. Next, you're in the Great Rm, featuring a Country, Island Kitchen, with ample cabinets & countertops. An L-Shaped Bkfast. bar opens to a lg Family Rm. Turnaround & see a Big Formal Dining. Living areas are tile floors, Vaulted, Crown-Mold, Plastered Ceilings, w/High-Hat recessed lighting. The Big Primary Bdrm & Walk-In closet has bamboo floors as do the 2 bdrms. The primary bath has dbl sinks w/Roman Tub, 2nd is a shower only. Toilets, sinks & Cent A/C are new. Windstorm protection is Impact Front & Garage doors w/steel panels all else. The Open Porch overlooks big back & side yards w/11+ fruit trees.
